<!doctype html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <meta name="description" content="A real-time, non-invasive tracker for agents." />
    <title>Burnlist — a real-time tracker for agents</title>
    <script>
      try {
        const theme = localStorage.getItem('starlight-theme');
        if (theme === 'light' || theme === 'dark') document.documentElement.dataset.theme = theme;
      } catch {}
    </script>
    <style>
      :root {
        --bg: #0b0d10;
        --bg-elev: #11141a;
        --panel: #11141a;
        --text: #e2e8f0;
        --muted: #94a3b8;
        --accent: #38bdf8;
        --accent-2: #7dd3fc;
        --hairline: rgba(255, 255, 255, .08);
        --hairline-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, .14);
        --code-bg: #0f1115;
        --hero-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #050a13, #0f1e31);
        --hero-border: rgba(56, 189, 248, .25);
        --font: 'Inter', system-ui, -apple-system, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif;
        --font-mono: 'SFMono-Regular', Consolas, 'Liberation Mono', Menlo, monospace;
        color-scheme: dark;
      }

      @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
        :root {
          --bg: #ffffff;
          --bg-elev: #f8fafc;
          --panel: #f8fafc;
          --text: #0f172a;
          --muted: #475569;
          --accent: #0284c7;
          --accent-2: #0369a1;
          --hairline: rgba(15, 23, 42, .1);
          --hairline-strong: rgba(15, 23, 42, .16);
          --code-bg: #f1f5f9;
          --hero-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
          --hero-border: rgba(2, 132, 199, .3);
          color-scheme: light;
        }
      }

      :root[data-theme='light'] {
        --bg: #ffffff;
        --bg-elev: #f8fafc;
        --panel: #f8fafc;
        --text: #0f172a;
        --muted: #475569;
        --accent: #0284c7;
        --accent-2: #0369a1;
        --hairline: rgba(15, 23, 42, .1);
        --hairline-strong: rgba(15, 23, 42, .16);
        --code-bg: #f1f5f9;
        --hero-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #eff6ff, #dbeafe);
        --hero-border: rgba(2, 132, 199, .3);
        color-scheme: light;
      }

      :root[data-theme='dark'] {
        --bg: #0b0d10;
        --bg-elev: #11141a;
        --panel: #11141a;
        --text: #e2e8f0;
        --muted: #94a3b8;
        --accent: #38bdf8;
        --accent-2: #7dd3fc;
        --hairline: rgba(255, 255, 255, .08);
        --hairline-strong: rgba(255, 255, 255, .14);
        --code-bg: #0f1115;
        --hero-gradient: linear-gradient(135deg, #050a13, #0f1e31);
        --hero-border: rgba(56, 189, 248, .25);
        color-scheme: dark;
      }

      * { box-sizing: border-box; }
      html { scroll-behavior: smooth; }
      body {
        margin: 0;
        min-width: 320px;
        overflow-x: hidden;
        background: var(--bg);
        color: var(--text);
        font-family: var(--font);
        line-height: 1.6;
      }
      a { color: inherit; text-decoration: none; }
      a:focus-visible {
        outline: 3px solid var(--accent);
        outline-offset: 3px;
      }
      .skip-link {
        position: absolute;
        left: -9999px;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 100;
        background: var(--accent);
        color: #07131b;
        font-weight: 750;
        padding: .6rem 1rem;
        border-radius: 0 0 8px 0;
      }
      .skip-link:focus { left: 0; }
      .container { width: min(1120px, calc(100% - 40px)); margin-inline: auto; }
      .topbar {
        position: sticky;
        top: 0;
        z-index: 10;
        border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline);
        background: color-mix(in srgb, var(--bg) 92%, transparent);
        backdrop-filter: blur(14px);
      }
      .topbar-inner { min-height: 68px; display: flex; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 24px; }
      .brand { color: var(--accent-2); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: 1.1rem; font-weight: 800; letter-spacing: -.04em; }
      .nav { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; justify-content: flex-end; gap: 6px; }
      .nav a { border-radius: 999px; color: var(--muted); font-size: .9rem; font-weight: 650; padding: .38rem .72rem; }
      .nav a:hover { background: var(--bg-elev); color: var(--text); }
      main { padding: 56px 0 76px; }
      section { margin-top: 88px; scroll-margin-top: 88px; }
      .hero { margin-top: 0; border: 1px solid var(--hero-border); border-radius: 16px; background: var(--hero-gradient); padding: clamp(2.2rem, 7vw, 5.2rem); }
      .eyebrow { display: inline-flex; border: 1px solid var(--hero-border); border-radius: 999px; color: var(--accent-2); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .75rem; font-weight: 700; letter-spacing: .02em; padding: .38rem .7rem; }
      h1, h2, h3, p { margin-top: 0; }
      h1 { max-width: 700px; font-size: clamp(3rem, 9vw, 6rem); letter-spacing: -.065em; line-height: .98; margin: 1.05rem 0 .85rem; }
      h2 { font-size: clamp(1.7rem, 4vw, 2.45rem); letter-spacing: -.04em; line-height: 1.1; margin-bottom: .75rem; }
      h3 { font-size: 1.08rem; letter-spacing: -.02em; margin-bottom: .5rem; }
      .tagline { color: var(--accent-2); font-size: clamp(1.25rem, 2.5vw, 1.7rem); font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: .8rem; }
      .intro { color: var(--muted); font-size: 1.06rem; max-width: 760px; }
      .actions { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .75rem; margin-top: 1.8rem; }
      .button { border: 1px solid var(--hairline-strong); border-radius: 999px; font-weight: 750; padding: .68rem 1rem; transition: transform .15s ease, background .15s ease; }
      .button:hover { transform: translateY(-1px); background: var(--bg-elev); }
      .button.primary { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: #07131b; }
      .button.primary:hover { background: var(--accent-2); border-color: var(--accent-2); }
      @media (prefers-color-scheme: light) {
        .button.primary { background: #0369a1; border-color: #0369a1; color: #fff; }
        .button.primary:hover { background: #075985; border-color: #075985; }
      }
      :root[data-theme='dark'] .button.primary { background: var(--accent); border-color: var(--accent); color: #07131b; }
      :root[data-theme='dark'] .button.primary:hover { background: var(--accent-2); border-color: var(--accent-2); }
      :root[data-theme='light'] .button.primary { background: #0369a1; border-color: #0369a1; color: #fff; }
      :root[data-theme='light'] .button.primary:hover { background: #075985; border-color: #075985; }
      .section-lede { color: var(--muted); max-width: 680px; }
      .grid { display: grid; grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 16px; margin-top: 1.8rem; }
      @media (min-width: 620px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr); } }
      @media (min-width: 1040px) { .grid { grid-template-columns: repeat(5, 1fr); } }
      .card { border: 1px solid var(--hairline); border-radius: 14px; background: var(--panel); padding: 1.35rem; }
      .card h3 { color: var(--accent-2); }
      .card p { color: var(--muted); font-size: .94rem; margin-bottom: 0; }
      code { font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .92em; }
      .loop { border: 1px solid var(--hairline); border-radius: 16px; background: var(--panel); padding: clamp(1.25rem, 4vw, 2.1rem); }
      .steps { list-style: none; padding: 0; display: grid; grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); align-items: center; gap: 10px; margin: 1.5rem 0; }
      .step { display: flex; align-items: center; gap: 10px; color: var(--accent-2); font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .92rem; font-weight: 750; white-space: nowrap; }
      .step:not(:last-child)::after { content: '→'; color: var(--muted); font-family: var(--font); font-size: 1.2rem; margin-left: auto; }
      .loop p { color: var(--muted); max-width: 70ch; margin-bottom: .9rem; }
      .flow-caption { color: var(--accent-2) !important; font-family: var(--font-mono); font-size: .85rem; font-weight: 700; margin-bottom: 0 !important; }
      .install-card { border: 1px solid var(--hairline); border-radius: 16px; background: var(--panel); overflow: hidden; }
      pre { max-width: 100%; overflow-x: auto; margin: 0; background: var(--code-bg); border-bottom: 1px solid var(--hairline); padding: 1.25rem 1.4rem; }
      pre code { color: var(--text); font-size: .96rem; }
      .install-copy { padding: 1.35rem; }
      .install-copy p { color: var(--muted); margin-bottom: .85rem; }
      .text-link { color: var(--accent-2); font-weight: 750; }
      .text-link:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
      footer { border-top: 1px solid var(--hairline); color: var(--muted); font-size: .88rem; padding: 28px 0; }
      .footer-inner { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; align-items: center; justify-content: space-between; gap: 14px; }
      .footer-links { display: flex; gap: 18px; }
      .footer-links a:hover { color: var(--accent-2); }

      @media (max-width: 960px) {
        main { padding-top: 36px; }
        section { margin-top: 64px; }
      }
      @media (max-width: 640px) {
        .container { width: min(100% - 28px, 1120px); }
        .topbar-inner { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; gap: 8px; padding: 13px 0; }
        .nav { justify-content: flex-start; margin-left: -.72rem; }
        .hero { padding: 2rem 1.35rem; }
        .steps { grid-template-columns: 1fr; gap: 8px; }
        .step:not(:last-child)::after { content: '↓'; margin-left: 8px; }
        .footer-inner { align-items: flex-start; flex-direction: column; }
      }
      @media (prefers-reduced-motion: reduce) {
        html { scroll-behavior: auto; }
        .button { transition: none; }
        .button:hover { transform: none; }
      }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <a class="skip-link" href="#main-content">Skip to content</a>
    <header class="topbar">
      <div class="container topbar-inner">
        <a class="brand" href="/" aria-label="Burnlist home">burnlist</a>
        <nav class="nav" aria-label="Primary navigation">
          <a href="/getting-started">Docs</a>
          <a href="/cli">CLI</a>
          <a href="/ovens">Ovens</a>
          <a href="/dashboard">Dashboard</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/layoutit/burnlist">GitHub</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main id="main-content" class="container">
      <section class="hero" aria-labelledby="page-title">
        <span class="eyebrow">Zero runtime dependencies · pure Node · MIT</span>
        <h1 id="page-title">Burnlist</h1>
        <p class="tagline">A real-time, non-invasive tracker for agents.</p>
        <p class="intro">A repo-local, shrinking Markdown checklist that renders live progress in a local observer dashboard. Burnlist owns task state — not your implementation, tests, or delivery.</p>
        <div class="actions" aria-label="Get started">
          <a class="button primary" href="/getting-started">Read the docs</a>
          <a class="button" href="#install">Install</a>
          <a class="button" href="https://github.com/layoutit/burnlist">GitHub</a>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="surfaces-title">
        <h2 id="surfaces-title">One tracker, five surfaces</h2>
        <p class="section-lede">The same shrinking queue gives agents, repositories, and observers a clear, local view of the work.</p>
        <div class="grid">
          <article class="card"><h3>CLI</h3><p>One command, <code>burnlist</code>, launches the loopback dashboard. Lifecycle verbs (<code>new</code>, <code>ready</code>, <code>start</code>, <code>burn</code>, <code>close</code>) plus protocol helpers (<code>--check</code>, <code>--digest</code>, <code>--stamp</code>) drive the burndown. Run <code>burnlist --help</code> for the full surface.</p></article>
          <article class="card"><h3>Dashboard</h3><p>A read-only web observer. It scans the <code>notes/burnlists/</code> lifecycle folders across your registered repos and refreshes automatically. It never mutates canonical task state.</p></article>
          <article class="card"><h3>Ovens</h3><p>Declarative, non-executable recipes for a Burn: two files — <code>instructions.md</code> (outcome + evidence rules) and <code>detail.json</code> (grid, widgets, bindings). Four built-in Ovens ship: Checklist, Differential Testing, Streaming Diff, and Performance Tracing.</p></article>
          <article class="card"><h3>Skills</h3><p>A single agent skill owns the full Burnlist lifecycle — creation, hardening, execution, and maintenance. It installs globally under <code>$HOME/.agents/skills</code>.</p></article>
          <article class="card"><h3>Hooks</h3><p><code>burnlist hooks install --agent codex,claude</code> merges Streaming Diff commands into <code>.codex/hooks.json</code> and <code>.claude/settings.json</code>, preserving your existing hook entries.</p></article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section aria-labelledby="loop-title">
        <div class="loop">
          <h2 id="loop-title">How the loop works</h2>
          <ol class="steps" aria-label="Burnlist folder lifecycle">
            <li class="step">draft/</li><li class="step">ready/</li><li class="step">inprogress/</li><li class="step">completed/</li>
          </ol>
          <p>Ready work moves to <code>inprogress</code> before execution and to <code>completed</code> once the active queue is empty. Each active item is validated before it leaves the checklist: the agent appends a terse completion record, deletes the item, then re-checks the Burnlist. <code>burnlist.md</code> is the canonical shrinking queue; <code>goal.md</code> holds the stable contract.</p>
          <p class="flow-caption">new → ready → start → burn → close</p>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section id="install" aria-labelledby="install-title">
        <h2 id="install-title">Install</h2>
        <div class="install-card">
          <pre><code>npm install --global burnlist
burnlist</code></pre>
          <div class="install-copy">
            <p>Requires Node.js 18 or newer. The global package installs the <code>burnlist</code> command and registers the bundled agent skill. Run <code>burnlist</code> from any project to open the dashboard on loopback.</p>
            <a class="text-link" href="/getting-started">Read the getting-started guide →</a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer>
      <div class="container footer-inner">
        <span>Burnlist · MIT License</span>
        <nav class="footer-links" aria-label="Footer navigation">
          <a href="/getting-started">Docs</a>
          <a href="https://github.com/layoutit/burnlist">GitHub</a>
        </nav>
      </div>
    </footer>
  </body>
